    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine starts and runs, though it could benefit from a tune-up to improve its overall performance. Cosmetically, there are several noticeable dings and scratches on the exterior, and the interior shows moderate wear, including some staining on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. While it is currently drivable, a thorough mechanical inspection is recommended to address minor fluid leaks and aging suspension components. It\u2019s a reliable foundation for anyone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
